OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry start, gradually
OL,6,Fbrightening up with some warm sunny
OL,7,Fintervals, but then scattered showers
OL,8,Fbreaking out, which could turn heavy
OL,9,Fand thundery by the afternoon. Winds
OL,10,Fwill be light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome heavy showers this
OL,13,Fevening in north, mainly Angus, these
OL,14,Fturning lighter and more scattered
OL,15,Ftonight with a few clear intervals
OL,16,Fpossible.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FA bright start with just
OL,19,Fthe odd shower. Turning cloudier in
OL,20,Fthe afternoon with some outbreaks of
OL,21,Frain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
