OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FChangeable through this period with a
OL,7,Fmix of bright spells and showers,
OL,8,Fthese heavy and thundery over Tayside
OL,9,Fon Thursday.
